Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:15.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}不断孕育出仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.67,0:02:18.45,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}知晓刻骨铭心的痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:21.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}你那份坚强
